{"tid":1506073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［置頂］中後排指令及行動檢討","createTime":"2019-08-25T16:57:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T08:15:08.000Z","uid":27203,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"9b71f8a2b4878c9168463420e026c708b65767e2","tid":1506073,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:57:19.000Z","msg":"每一日都見到前線因為中後排唔夠位而比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中後排有佢既價值所以唔好唔出<br />\n但係指令可以清晰啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再嗌 走呀 製造不必要恐慌</span></span><br />\n大家唔會知要走幾快架<br />\n<br />\n不如統一指令啦各位 <br />\n<br />\n退=慢慢向後退 真係慢慢行 調整防線位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跑= 同我用你最快既速度向後跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n散開啲= 每個人最少一隻手位 伸開手要掂唔到人 唔係不斷向後退呀唔該 今日退撚到大東北咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n走個陣唔想走失就拉住前面個袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到有好撚多人組左好多人既戰隊 一堆人企埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到根本逼撚埋一齊 散唔開<br />\n唔該就住性別 逃跑路線 同心態分2-3人一小隊咁企 2-3個人齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪撚再堆埋一齊/一字排開6-7條友<br />\n你咁樣走又阻頭阻勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">永遠支持前線<br />\n核彈都唔割<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"02eb3ace4cd70e04a9e7a1111f5f7c1e854374b3","tid":1506073,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:57:33.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"cc527639052610bfa65ac5e0dc7db121b79f115a","tid":1506073,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:57:43.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"e79697b7509d03fb05482b2afc53315a75f701dc","tid":1506073,"u