00Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143b932ae4cfcac535ae7bcf16ddaec15833ade6","tid":1506073,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0ad3623eef26c457b6833652133021d0562a996","tid":1506073,"uid":56428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:12:48.000Z","msg":"現場唔夠喇叭同人員傳指令"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:13:48.000Z","msg":"但係叫人退呢個指令本身冇快慢程度之分<br />\n所以要統一同清晰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981d01b5846ed0c83e3bd9deee72c3e4a1224b76","tid":1506073,"uid":206812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:13:54.000Z","msg":"家母一路睇電視 見好多人爬山嘅時候<br />\n俾狗咬住個背囊走唔甩 咬到好傷好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以用師奶思想 建議大家<br />\n行山嘅時候 個書包入面裝水裝紙巾好喇<br />\n至於你啲身分證 或者其他重要嘢<br />\n有腰包就放腰包（要戴係面衫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">裡面</span></span>啊懵佬）<br />\n無就好似呀婆咁 著條有袋/拉鍊嘅背心底衫喇<br />\n你知啲動物好鍾意咬住個袋唔放 唔俾你走<br />\n只要你個袋無重要嘢 就可以嚟一招<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">金蟬脫殼</span></span>"},{"pid":"167a313638357e1be65989026f54439c7cef831e","tid":1506073,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7d653ac19cb8df654950e9111b1008315e37d8","tid":1506073,"uid":198783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3864bcb98e54591106e0662297d1d4c59cc737","tid":1506073,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81897fe6fa4f9ed6a8674b0ed7edfb8eca84f3c9","tid":1506073,"uid":198783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:14:47.000Z","